  <brief_title>Inflammatory Effects of a Lung Recruitment Manoeuvre</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective, Open, Uncontrolled, Non-randomized and Monocentric Trial on the Efficacy and the Inflammatory Effects of a Lung Recruitment Manoeuvre in Mechanical Ventilated Patients With Respiratory Failure</official_title>
