  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Mechanical Ventilation

          -  Arterial catheter inserted

          -  Hypoxemic respiratory failure (Pa02/FiO2 &lt;300)

          -  Radiological evidence of atelectasis or pulmonary infiltrates in the CXR

          -  Informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Elevated intracranial pressure &gt;25 mmHg

          -  Bronchopulmonary fistula

          -  Emphysema

          -  Kidney or Liver failure
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
